  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Define the frequency and survival pattern of cardiac arrests in relation to the hospital day
      of event and etiology of arrest.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Define the frequency and survival pattern of cardiac arrests in relation with event and
      etiology of arrest.

      Investigators aims to evaluate the outcome of in-hospital cardiac arrests, focusing on the
      relationship between etiology and outcome.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
